	(60,1,'2013-10-07 05:39:17','2013-10-07 05:39:17','<div>\r\n<h1>Agency Background</h1>\r\nFounded in 2006, AG Design Group, Inc. is an award winning, full service Creative Agency and Marketing Firm. AG Design Group, Inc. is a Women-Owned and Minority-Owned Small Business headquartered in Walnut Creek, California. We are located steps from San Francisco and Silicon Valley in the heart of Northern Californias Bay Area. We have proven capabilities in executing coast-to-coast projects for clients from San Francisco to New York, and have partnered with teams in Europe and Asia.\r\n\r\nOur Team strives to achieve professional design, direction, and communication success for our clients. Our success and the success of our clients, take the form of company growth, identification, brand recognition, design innovation, and return on investment. We specialize in tailoring our services to our clients needs  combining innovative approaches with unparalleled resources, make AG Design Group a premier choice in the Creative Marketing industry.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>WE PROVIDE OUR CLIENTS WITH THE FOLLOWING BENEFITS:</strong>\r\n+ Graphic Design and website design that out performs the industry average\r\n+ Unparalleled knowledge of current industry standards, techniques, and technologies\r\n+ Innovative approaches to marketing campaigns through targeted communication design\r\n+ Accessibility that exceeds expectations\r\n+ High accountability and measurable results\r\n+ Dedicated staff that are educated, proven, and who immerse themselves in the clients business, goals,philosophy, and principles\r\n+ A design firm committed to developing long term relationships with our clients','About','','publish','open','open','','about-agd','','','2013-12-11 08:41:47','2013-12-11 08:41:47','',0,'http://www.agdesigngroup.com/dev/?page_id=60',1,'page','',0),
